Twitte - simple Twitter bot using Tweepy

Can favorite tweets from given searches.
Can tweet random or timed prepared tweets.
Can handle multiple accounts.

Tweepy version >=3.1.0 needed.


authorize.py - util to obtain user approval for Twitte
./authorize.py instance_example

Crontab example:
# different frequencies used to mimic human behaviour ;)

*/3 8-21 * * * user /path/twitte/twitte.py /path/twitte/ >> /path/twitte/dbg.log 2>&1
*/18 6,7,22,23 * * * user /path/twitte/twitte.py /path/twitte/ >> /path/twitte/dbg.log 2>&1
